{"title":"春城新歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春城新歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新景\t苏宗仁　王慧秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食堂里饭菜热腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹桌又端凳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大嫂笑颜开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席间穿梭行……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桌旁有人问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为啥这样起劲？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当这么大的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不高兴！”\t缝纫组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂灯结彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜气洋洋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲锣又打鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭炮连声响……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“妈妈，这么热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家娶新娘？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子，别嚷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你看！缝纫机进新房”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理发室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张家小明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王家小华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个争坐镜台前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要大姐理发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白帽白罩衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大姐笑得像朵花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧手使夹剪——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人容光焕发……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托儿所"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老李下班回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门内静悄悄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“素兰呢？哪里去了——”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房里摇篮排成行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她坐床边把手摇："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘘！别吵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们才睡着……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两次作客"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王功藩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月前我路过北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺便拜望了大婶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她围着锅台打转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"床上的孩子弹腿啼喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大婶忙给孩子穿衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把换下的尿布洗净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炉上饭锅冒出焦味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得她热汗浇头怨声阵阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我又从北京路过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺便又去看望大婶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见她家的房门虚掩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满屋清洁却不见人影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正在暗地纳闷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东邻奶奶过来搭岔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你大婶在民办鞋厂工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也刚把她屋里拾掇干净”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老奶奶的话尚未落音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走廊里响起格格笑声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群妇女下班归来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大婶急步踏入门坎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大婶的脸上红光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又说又笑还双手指划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看她那股高兴劲儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛一位少女青春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等我插话开腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她紧把我的手搀起："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“走！到咱居民食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你吃一顿饺子！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我尾随大婶穿过街心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道旁的行人面容可亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棵棵白杨吐出碧绿新芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心呀像春潮翻滚……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}